data.enText: an organ in a person's or an animal's body that produces a substance for the body to use. There are many different glands in the body.

tr: any of various organs that synthesize substances needed by the body and release it through ducts or directly into the bloodstream

value.def: A gland is an organ in the body which produces chemical substances for the body to use or get rid of.

example.ex: ...the hormones secreted by our endocrine glands.
example.tran: 人体内分泌腺分泌的荷尔蒙
